from\": 2221, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"a nursery\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are starting to gain more information regarding elite sport and motherhood, and there is emerging evidence on training for elite sport participation during pregnancy.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"motherhood\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"emerging evidence\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport participation\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there is much room for improvement.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much room\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"improvement\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Health Organization's recommendations for physical activity suggest that allpregnant women, without contraindication, should meet 150 minutes of moderate-physical activity per week.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Health_Organization\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.890948799039679e-51, \"text\": \"World Health Organization\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Health_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Health_Organization\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"physical activity\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"allpregnant women\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"contraindication\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"150 minutes\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"moderate-physical activity\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, the Canadian guideline document for physical activity during pregnancy has recommended that physical activity be accumulated over a minimum of three days per week, and should incorporate a variety of aerobic and resistance exercises.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2848, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9930627625975322, \"rank\": 0.006985698831595922, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"physical activity\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"physical activity\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"aerobic and resistance exercises\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Physical activity during pregnancy can lead to a multitude of health benefits for both mother and baby, such as decreased risk of pre-eclampsia, gestational diabetes, hypertension, excessive gestational weight gain, postpartum depression and newborn complications.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Physical activity\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"a multitude\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"health benefits\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"both mother\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"baby\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3181}, {\"ngram\": \"decreased risk\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"pre\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"gestational diabetes\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"hypertension\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"excessive gestational weight gain\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"postpartum depression\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"newborn complications\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regular physical activity has no adverse effects on birth weight or does not increase the risk of stillborn birth.\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Regular physical activity\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"no adverse effects\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"birth weight\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3438}, {\"ngram\": \"stillborn birth\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, the IOC assembled an international expert committee and published a set of recommendations for training during pregnancy for recreational and elite-level athletes.\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3473, \"end\": 3476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.328313728324202e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an international expert committee\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"recommendations\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3559}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"recreational and elite-level athletes\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These guidelines advise that, barring contraindications like pre-eclampsia or hypertension, women can safely continue with their regular aerobic activity while monitoring for important symptoms - like vaginal bleeding or frequent contractions - that would signal the need to modify or stop the activity and seek medical advice.\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These guidelines\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"contraindications\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"pre\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"eclampsia\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3708}, {\"ngram\": \"hypertension\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"their regular aerobic activity\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3787}, {\"ngram\": \"important symptoms\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3827}, {\"ngram\": \"vaginal bleeding\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"frequent contractions\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3876}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3905}, {\"ngram\": \"the activity\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3936}, {\"ngram\": \"medical advice\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The guidelines recommend a maximum intensity of equal to or greater than 90 per cent of the maximum rate of oxygen consumption during exercise (also termed VO2 max).\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 4128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4119, \"end\": 4126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"VO2 max\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The guidelines\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum intensity\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 4007}, {\"ngram\": \"equal to or greater than 90 per cent\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the maximum rate\", \"from\": 4051, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"oxygen consumption\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4089}, {\"ngram\": \"exercise\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there has not been much research on athletes whose baseline VO2 max is already significantly higher than the general population.\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"VO2 max\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/VO2_max\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much research\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4170}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"the general population\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elite athletes have reported uncertainty about training through pregnancy.\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Elite athletes\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainty\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4308}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They exercise well above the 150 minutes per week, often at a vigorous intensity, causing some to question the relevance of these recommendations to them.\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 150 minutes\", \"from\": 4368, \"to\": 4383}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4392}, {\"ngram\": \"a vigorous intensity\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4423}, {\"ngram\": \"the relevance\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"these recommendations\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, a study conducted on 42 elite-level runners during pregnancy found that while their training volume decreased from the first to the third trimester, it was still two to four times higher than current guidelines.\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"a study\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"42 elite-level runners\", \"from\": 4534, \"to\": 4556}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4573}, {\"ngram\": \"their training volume\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"the third trimester\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4660}, {\"ngram\": \"current guidelines\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another study demonstrated that high-intensity interval training, which takes place at above 90 per cent of maximum heart rate, was well-tolerated by both medically screened mothers and fetuses for acute sessions and short periods of time.\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another study\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4739}, {\"ngram\": \"high-intensity interval training\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4790}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4809}, {\"ngram\": \"above 90 per cent\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum heart rate\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4852}, {\"ngram\": \"both medically screened mothers\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"fetuses\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"acute sessions\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4938}, {\"ngram\": \"short periods\", \"from\": 4943, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4960, \"to\": 4964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More research is needed to provide better guidance on exercise frequency, intensity and duration for pregnant athletes, as the current guidelines may be relatively conservative for elite athletes.\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 5163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More research\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"better guidance\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5017}, {\"ngram\": \"exercise frequency\", \"from\": 5021, \"to\": 5039}, {\"ngram\": \"intensity\", \"from\": 5041, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"duration\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5063}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnant athletes\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"the current guidelines\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5112}, {\"ngram\": \"elite athletes\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past few Olympic Games, mother-athlete advocates have highlighted the difficult decisions athletes feel they must make when training during pregnancy.\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past few Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"mother-athlete advocates\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5222}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficult decisions athletes\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, some athletes struggle with the societal pressure to choose between becoming pregnant or being an athlete - a choice male athletes never have to make.\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5337}, {\"ngram\": \"some athletes\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"the societal pressure\", \"from\": 5367, \"to\": 5388}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5444}, {\"ngram\": \"a choice male athletes\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes also expressed concerns around pregnancy planning, fertility, pregnancy disclosure, discrimination, safety while training, and funding support.\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5498}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy planning\", \"from\": 5530, \"to\": 5548}, {\"ngram\": \"fertility\", \"from\": 5550, \"to\": 5559}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy disclosure\", \"from\": 5561, \"to\": 5581}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A follow-up study conducted with coaches and health-care professionals working with pregnant and postpartum athletes revealed similar themes.\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A follow-up study\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5684}, {\"ngram\": \"health-care professionals\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5714}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnant and postpartum athletes\", \"from\": 5728, \"to\": 5760}, {\"ngram\": \"similar themes\", \"from\": 5770, \"to\": 5784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This included a lack of female-athlete reproductive research, a need for evidence-informed education and training, open communication to support athlete-centred care, and better essential supports and policy changes to support pregnant or postpartum athletes.\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 6045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5806}, {\"ngram\": \"female-athlete reproductive research\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5846}, {\"ngram\": \"a need\", \"from\": 5848, \"to\": 5854}, {\"ngram\": \"evidence-informed education\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5886}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5899}, {\"ngram\": \"open communication\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5919}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete-centred care\", \"from\": 5931, \"to\": 5951}, {\"ngram\": \"better essential supports\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5982}, {\"ngram\": \"policy changes\", \"from\": 5987, \"to\": 6001}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnant or postpartum athletes\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the right supports in place, athletes can continue to train during pregnancy with medical support, and excel after birth.\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right supports\", \"from\": 6052, \"to\": 6070}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 6074, \"to\": 6079}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6089}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6128}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 6167, \"to\": 6172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, as with pregnancy and postpartum care, there is still work to be done to improve athlete care and support.\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6200}, {\"ngram\": \"postpartum care\", \"from\": 6205, \"to\": 6220}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6241}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete care\", \"from\": 6264, \"to\": 6276}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 6281, \"to\": 6288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need more high-quality evidence to inform evidence-based guidelines for elite sport participation and training through pregnancy and return to sport postpartum, with improved sport policy.\", \"from\": 6291, \"to\": 6482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more high-quality evidence\", \"from\": 6299, \"to\": 6325}, {\"ngram\": \"evidence-based guidelines\", \"from\": 6336, \"to\": 6361}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport participation\", \"from\": 6366, \"to\": 6391}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 6396, \"to\": 6404}, {\"ngram\": \"pregnancy\", \"from\": 6413, \"to\": 6422}, {\"ngram\": \"sport postpartum\", \"from\": 6437, \"to\": 6453}, {\"ngram\": \"improved sport policy\", \"from\": 6460, \"to\": 6481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will, in turn, promote longevity in sport.\", \"from\": 6483, \"to\": 6530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6501}, {\"ngram\": \"longevity\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6520}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jenna Schulz is Physiotherapist and Postdoctoral Fellow, Fowler Kennedy Sport Medicine Clinic, Western University.\", \"from\": 6532, \"to\": 6646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6532, \"end\": 6537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"score\": 0.9432482743190117, \"rank\": 0.0592503177684967, \"text\": \"Jenna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\"}, {\"begin\": 6589, \"end\": 6595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A_Dictionary_of_Modern_English_Usage\", \"score\": 0.9998013724278648, \"rank\": 0.00019787532617917842, \"text\": \"Fowler\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A_Dictionary_of_Modern_English_Usage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A_Dictionary_of_Modern_English_Usage\"}, {\"begin\": 6596, \"end\": 6603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.9999999140254695, \"rank\": 8.592542255895255e-08, \"text\": \"Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\"}, {\"begin\": 6627, \"end\": 6645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Western_Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9999999990091055, \"rank\": 9.908520957672471e-10, \"text\": \"Western University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Western_Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Western_Ontario\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jane Thornton is a Sport Medicine Physician at Western University and a former Canadian Olympic rower.\", \"from\": 6647, \"to\": 6749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6647, \"end\": 6660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Thornton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jane Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q190